1. Install node_exporters to all hosts
2. Install Prometheus to one host
3. Variables:
  - Prometheus version
  - Monitored hosts
4. Prometheus and Exporters should run with own users
5. Only fqdn in Prometheus config, no IPs allowed
6. Prometheus web interface is at prometheus.<your-startup-fqdn>:9090
7. No parameters for ansible-playbook command
